By":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:08:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c405d53437e95ee7d37b78ac97caf4559aeaae76","tid":1982370,"uid":39872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"第一個可能性最高，係無棋見步行步，最重要就係保住黨o既絕對領導同時亦慢慢走向衰亡<br />\n鎖國係可以預期，人口將會十年間跌到得返十億，因為係脫離全球化o既代價，大陸經濟體萎縮、同要再次重建自給自足體系並非一朝一夕"},{"pid":"25f885a4b5f35682e92b821d1623acac0996b1cb","tid":1982370,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0e571f6f72f3ed9d847fb0eca442bcdedaf14c","tid":1982370,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261e92bc0e15082f33e5940211f084b99d96c0f7","tid":1982370,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"(遊戲戰線)如何潑火令中共永久封鎖STEAM<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1982465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1982465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家幫推有用post"},{"pid":"590a495f5d393478a6c435fe889102f5fe7318d5","tid":1982370,"uid":193697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"157c5ddc65560f2abfe9a4d882d16392733e20b5","tid":1982370,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59585b43804ec429fbe429458ce6c2bf8628e9ea","tid":1982370,"uid":138092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"目前最緊要嘅係要再進一步利用香港人兩文三語嘅能力，去瓦解支那嘅外宣，爭取多啲唔同國際勢力嘅支持同埋揭露支那嘅陰險面目。支聯辦做嘅任何一件事，都無限放大上綱上線令佢哋疲於解話。唔好鬥黃，但係要繼續鬥紅鬥藍鬥到佢哋死無葬身之地。繼續針對政權，針對黑警。<br />\n<br />\n支那呢啲<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">密集式維穩</span></ins></span>需要動用極大嘅資源同財力，睇下黑警嘅OT錢攞咗幾多就知，俾班畜牲攞一年OT，之後仲可以攞幾多年而保證民間怨言唔會持續高漲？武漢肺炎搞到全世界經濟咁，佢哋再有錢又可以玩幾耐？細水長流同佢慢慢玩，盡量耗曬支那同港共政府投放嘅維穩資源。同時呢段時間都要籌劃下以後嘅街頭抗爭點樣持續。"},{"pid":"f37dde893a89ebc370deef330606fde7f890e489","tid":1982370,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062e1641366cd9bfb38f5b18ffab27b8ca0ab5d0","tid":1982370,"uid":146030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"最緊要將香港同1949上海相提並論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2dba3fd1ce18a4304bba53ecedd4f191301f07","tid":1982370,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"乜都試下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a7574ee6345e37c3b317e576a4beae9f75e104","tid":1982370,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Twitter 國際戰線需要你<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\nTwitter文宣組<br />\n戰線台 @twittermansyunzou <br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線 @reddithk_channel<br />\n文宣 @hkstandstrong_promo_int @guardiansofhongkong<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=ca8dd487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n做任務，推任務，整圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cm4FxNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCm4FxNr.jpg&h=15d08911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJWHL7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft